content:
O bahenních rostlinách

The book describes celandine, beggartick and fool's parsley, as well as the methods of obtaining alchemical ingredients from these plants.

The book describes plants that grow in bažiny. It is a valuable resource for those who wish to recognize these plants and obtain alchemical ingredients from them.
